race.comment: MAMA MARGE (1) built on a nice second two starts back at Mountaineer Park (Dirt) with success as favourite over 1106m at Mountaineer Park (Dirt) three-and-a-half weeks ago, getting home by 2.75 lengths. Sunday Jr Diaz scored on her last time and retains the ride. Taking on a better field but she is up to the task. SMOKIN LADY (6) last appeared two weeks ago over 1408m at this track when she finished second. This is her first run for the Joanna Boggs stable. Expecting a bright start for the new mentor. BULL'S LEGACY (3) lines up on the back of a 16 length sixth over 1408m at this track. Key contender. TRUE INDY (7) went around over this course and distance last time and led from the outset to score by 1.75 lengths. F Peltroche who has four wins when partnering stays on. Don't underestimate.
